ckground-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 25px; font: 14px/25px  Microsoft Yahei , tahoma, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">请填写附件中的报名表发送至联系邮箱，邮件标题格式为&ldquo;棋类比赛报名+单位+姓名&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 25px; font: 14px/25px  Microsoft Yahei , tahoma, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">六、 比赛规则：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 25px; font: 14px/25px  Microsoft Yahei , tahoma, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">待定</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 25px; font: 14px/25px  Microsoft Yahei , tahoma, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">附件：<a href=\"http://www.shstzz.com/download/20140905.xlsx\" style=\"color: rgb(11,43,55); text-decoration: none\">&ldquo;金领驿站&rdquo;迎国庆棋类比赛报名表</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 25px; font: 14px/25px  Microsoft Yahei , tahoma, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">集团公司党委办公室</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 25px; font: 14px/25px  Microsoft Yahei , tahoma, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2014年9月4日</p>', '0', '2014-09-11', 'upfiles/CR-5aRpXes3tr');
